710783f-b.text:
Twelfth Avenue, east side, south from West 49th to West 48th Streets, showing the old and the new frontage after the widening of this Avenue. A swath of land was sliced off of this side to provide for this marginal improvement. Close observation will show several structures remaining.

May 21, 1936

P. L. Sperr
